--[=[
	@class Highlight

	hover žčú BackgroundColor3Ž•ľ ŪäłžúąŪēėŽäĒ attachmentžěÖŽčąŽč§.

	```luau
	Frame({
		Attach = {
			Highlight({ NormalColor = ..., HighlightColor = ... }),
		},
	})
	```
